Concepts
-Loose Coupling
-Well-defined, but complex
-Reusable components
-Acts as a hub/router in your app that all communication goes through

Design
-Interface Based with a Concrete Class
-Minimizes Inheritance
-Mediator knows about all of the colleagues
-Mediator, concrete mediator

 Contrast
 -Mediator                      Observer
 Defines Interaction          One to Many
 Object Decoupling            Object Decoupling
 More Specific                More Generic